javax.jdo.metadata

Interface TypeMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Metadata
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClassMetadata, InterfaceMetadata

    public interface TypeMetadata
extends Metadata
    Represents a class or interface. Extended for the specifics of those cases.
    Since:
    3.0
